msgstr "它不易燃，但装着计时器。"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WOLFGANG.DESCRIBE.WATCH_CONTAINER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WOLFGANG.DESCRIBE.WATCH_CONTAINER"
