msgstr "装小钟表的结实盒子！"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WENDY.DESCRIBE.WATCH_CONTAINER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WENDY.DESCRIBE.WATCH_CONTAINER"
