msgstr "好好保管怀表。"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WAXWELL.DESCRIBE.WATCH_CONTAINER
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.WAXWELL.DESCRIBE.WATCH_CONTAINER"
